README

This website presents a canvas game called Cubic Battle.
Just play with your cursor or your finger.

Rules :
- Targets : 
	- Blue target need 1 shot to be destroyed.
	- Purple target need 4 shots to be destroyed.
	- Yellow target need 8 shots to be destroyed.
	- The first boss appear when you reach 900 points and need 80 shots to be destroyed.
	- The second boss appear when you reach 2200 points and need 120 shots to be destroyed.
	- Pink target is a LIFE ! GO GET IT !
	- Green target is the bonus ! Take it and enjoy the DOUBLE FIRE !

- More target you destroy more you gain points. 
- More point you more targets spawn and more their speed increase.
- CARE ! Don't get touch by the targets or you will lose a life.
- If a target escape from the playable area you will lose points (-2).

Features :
- The game is responsive and playable on mobile, tablet, desktop.
- High score is saved in local storage.

Link :
For an easiest test on mobile and tablet go on : www.arthurbalossini.com/cubicbattle


